00:02:42.280 --> 00:02:44.610
"Why should doing good come with a price?"

00:02:44.800 --> 00:02:46.329
"How does that make sense?"

00:02:47.190 --> 00:02:47.800
I said,

00:02:48.360 --> 00:02:49.590
"People who do bad things"

00:02:49.590 --> 00:02:50.400
"are bad."

00:02:50.840 --> 00:02:53.150
"How could they possibly
not pay a price for it?"

00:02:53.150 --> 00:02:54.150
"Even if the good"

00:02:54.590 --> 00:02:55.960
"must pay,"

00:02:55.960 --> 00:02:57.760
"their hearts remain at peace."

00:02:58.030 --> 00:03:00.030
"That's why choosing good is hard."

00:03:00.710 --> 00:03:01.870
Chunji fell silent,

00:03:02.000 --> 00:03:03.860
as if something had dawned on her.

00:03:04.680 --> 00:03:05.710
On March 16,

00:03:06.430 --> 00:03:08.590
while walking with Chunji
in the courtyard,

00:03:08.590 --> 00:03:09.590
Chunji said,

00:03:10.190 --> 00:03:13.800
"It feels like I haven't taken a walk
with my master in a long time."

00:03:13.800 --> 00:03:15.800
I felt a deep ache.

00:03:16.120 --> 00:03:17.910
Thinking back on everything,

00:03:18.680 --> 00:03:19.870
I regret that

00:03:20.190 --> 00:03:22.650
perhaps I didn't care enough
for my disciple,

00:03:22.650 --> 00:03:25.650
that I failed to win their trust.

00:03:26.030 --> 00:03:27.690
That is my fault as her master.

00:03:28.560 --> 00:03:31.190
Thankfully, it is not yet too late.

