00:04:10.150 --> 00:04:11.680
Throwing iron chopsticks?

00:04:11.880 --> 00:04:13.480
You've surely forgotten it.

00:04:18.040 --> 00:04:19.040
Master!

00:04:37.240 --> 00:04:38.510
Ms. Zhong
from the Central Plains Sword Alliance

00:04:38.510 --> 00:04:39.970
has always been my friend.

00:04:40.350 --> 00:04:41.880
It's only now that I realize

00:04:42.200 --> 00:04:43.810
she never wanted to be Ms. Zhong,

00:04:43.810 --> 00:04:44.360
♪ The breeze blows through the pleats ♪

00:04:44.360 --> 00:04:46.290
nor did she want to be called Zhong.

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:48.920
Since you're no longer willing to be

00:04:48.920 --> 00:04:50.159
your former self,

00:04:51.000 --> 00:04:52.040
why cling to

00:04:52.460 --> 00:04:54.020
old titles

00:04:54.750 --> 00:04:55.360
to cover up

00:04:55.360 --> 00:04:55.890
your heart that's slowly drifting away?

00:04:55.890 --> 00:04:58.310
♪ Water polishes the old ruts ♪

00:04:58.310 --> 00:04:59.720
Mr. Tang, do you remember

00:05:00.270 --> 00:05:01.870
the first time we met?

00:05:03.190 --> 00:05:05.050
What did you think of me back then?

00:05:06.870 --> 00:05:08.360
