00:05:08.360 --> 00:05:10.420
What a spirited and valiant heroine.

00:05:14.120 --> 00:05:14.800
And now?

00:05:16.000 --> 00:05:17.200
Do you still think so?

00:05:18.600 --> 00:05:20.630
♪ Trapped in the loop of loneliness ♪

00:05:20.630 --> 00:05:22.230
Wounds aren't frightening.

00:05:22.600 --> 00:05:24.000
What scares people

00:05:24.720 --> 00:05:25.600
is the pain.

00:05:26.670 --> 00:05:27.200
But one can't avoid treating wounds

00:05:27.200 --> 00:05:28.720
♪ Trapped in the loop of loneliness ♪

00:05:28.720 --> 00:05:30.120
just because it hurts.

00:05:30.950 --> 00:05:32.350
I'll enter the palace now

00:05:32.630 --> 00:05:34.560
and clarify everything to Mother.

